      <title>五角大楼面临国会不愿解决的华为困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/pentagon-has-a-huawei-dilemma-congress-doesn-t-want-to-solve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼面临一个问题：作为全球最大的雇主之一，如何避免与依赖中国华为技术有限公司（全球最大电信供应商）的公司做生意？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/pentagon-has-a-huawei-dilemma-congress-doesn-t-want-to-solve</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
